burn(uint256).notice: Burn a token - any game logic should be handled before this function.

getMintDirtCost(uint16).notice: Calculate the dirt minting cost: - the first 20% are paid in ETH - the next 20% are 20000 $DIRT - the next 40% are 40000 $DIRT - the final 20% are 80000 $DIRT

isWorm(uint256).notice: checks if a token is a Wizards

setMaxMintAmount(uint16).notice: Set the max mints per account during persale and per tx during public sale

setMintingStatus(bool).notice: sets the status of minting for public sale
